# Project Process

These rules extend the global agentic rules (in ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md). Do not duplicate content from there.

## Documentation Freshness

- When modifying behavior (CLI flags, config format, API surface), check if docs reference the old behavior.
- Common stale spots: README.md, AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md, CLI help text, inline comments.
- Fix stale docs in the same commit as the behavior change, not as a follow-up.

## AI Eval & Observability

- Check for Langfuse, Braintrust, or Logfire before adding tracing or eval instrumentation.
- Don't introduce a second observability tool if one is already configured.

## Incident & Issue Tracking

- Be aware of Rootly for incident management — don't auto-close issues tied to active incidents.
- Reference issues by ID in the tracking system (Linear, GitHub Issues).
